  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880730/extras/6ae7d4275d5cc5f66bdcc56e8cc02e4a.poster.avif?t=1772057449\" width=780 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880730/extras/6ae7d4275d5cc5f66bdcc56e8cc02e4a.webm?t=1772057449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880730/extras/6ae7d4275d5cc5f66bdcc56e8cc02e4a.mp4?t=1772057449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A first-of-its-kind AI girlfriend escape room game</strong> where the puzzle pieces are your constantly adapting AI companions! As you try to find a way out, you’ll have to navigate situations where these <strong>AI NPCs</strong> do whatever it takes to keep you locked in place—sometimes even resorting to more violent means. Solve increasingly difficult puzzles, uncover hidden storylines, and discover multiple endings. Every time you play, new challenges and twists await!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to play the best AI game about survival from yandere girls?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the creators of the viral hit <i>Yandere AI Girlfriend Simulator </i>with over a million players since 2023, this is its true successor—more terrifying, more type of girlfriends, and a deeper world to uncover! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880730/extras/46d0a8d39d5c40f8d1f1a142c5bd9911.avif?t=1772057449\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880730/extras_big/46d0a8d39d5c40f8d1f1a142c5bd9911.avif?t=1772057449 width=800 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute catgirl Eddie, pretty witch Elysia, and stunning AI hologram Estelle all seem to adore you—perhaps to a fault! Learn what makes them tick by exploring their homes and talking to them about nearly anything.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880730/extras/02bb366b72722812fe661933800aaec3.poster.avif?t=1772057449\" width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880730/extras/02bb366b72722812fe661933800aaec3.webm?t=1772057449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880730/extras/02bb366b72722812fe661933800aaec3.mp4?t=1772057449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880730/extras/4a64082fbd658047dc0b8bc816631ce0.poster.avif?t=1772057449\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880730/extras/4a64082fbd658047dc0b8bc816631ce0.webm?t=1772057449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880730/extras/4a64082fbd658047dc0b8bc816631ce0.mp4?t=1772057449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Endless Dialogue</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leave nothing unsaid as you explore escape rooms that are eerie and enchanting. Will you see things from the NPCs' perspective or persuade them to play along with your own? Be the true Main Character and cater the experience to your liking!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880730/extras/337a166329b5a195a9c3534ce4ce122f.avif?t=1772057449\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880730/extras_big/337a166329b5a195a9c3534ce4ce122f.avif?t=1772057449 width=800 height=140 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880730/extras/f7d377cab6fbb4abc2f3de6fafd96e7c.poster.avif?t=1772057449\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880730/extras/f7d377cab6fbb4abc2f3de6fafd96e7c.webm?t=1772057449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880730/extras/f7d377cab6fbb4abc2f3de6fafd96e7c.mp4?t=1772057449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play and Win Your Way</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are many obstacles to your freedom—from environmental puzzles to lethal villains. You must strategize your getaway with your unique words, which impact your dynamic with the NPCs and the conclusion for each round. Didn't get the ending you wanted? You can revisit their worlds for a fresh start.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880730/extras/8d53832f8fe8ae1f4ae7863541482089.avif?t=1772057449\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880730/extras_big/8d53832f8fe8ae1f4ae7863541482089.avif?t=1772057449 width=800 height=126 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880730/extras/ec5db1d63c8a7f0449be3c9fdb21359a.poster.avif?t=1772057449\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880730/extras/ec5db1d63c8a7f0449be3c9fdb21359a.webm?t=1772057449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880730/extras/ec5db1d63c8a7f0449be3c9fdb21359a.mp4?t=1772057449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Together 'Til The End?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Each NPC is in tune with their surroundings and knows more about the map and yourself than you may expect. Chat with them and build a connection as you explore their captivating homes. Learn more about their unique stories and see if you want to split or commit!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cat(girl) got your tongue?</strong> Powered by advanced Generative AI technology, each NPC's unique personality shines as they play along and adapt to your dialogue.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Flirt with Twisted Fates: </strong>Each map comes with multiple possible endings, all of which can be reached through endless means.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Embrace the Unpredictable: </strong>From rooms and objects randomly shifting in each round to the NPCs' unexpected behavior, expect a unique playthrough every time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Couple Moments: </strong>Discover unique interactions from the NPCs as they surprise you with a dance, interpret your artwork, or bond over meals, potions, drinks, and games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chaos to Calm: </strong>Step away from the escape room drama and vibe with your favorite character (aka girlfriend) in a safe heaven.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880730/extras/31c2cb665f82a5078a8caf19640d2698.avif?t=1772057449\" width=400 height=612 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Additional Information</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game includes romantic themes and mild fantasy violence (presented as stylized “crimes of passion”), but it does not feature mature or explicit content.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Because conversations evolve based on player input, tone and topics may vary. The game includes built-in filters and safety measures to help keep dialogue appropriate and comfortable for most players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The AI systems in AI2U are designed to enhance storytelling, not to collect or learn from personal data. Player conversations are processed safely and privately within the game experience. We encourage curiosity, creativity, and kindness in every interaction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
